OL,3,C'Lumbering dinosaur' HMRC becoming
OL,4,Cmore expensive and less trusted, say
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FThe tax system is becoming more
OL,8,Fexpensive and less trusted as HM
OL,9,FRevenue & Customs (HMRC) struggles to
OL,10,Fmodernise, a committee of MPs has
OL,11,Fwarned.
OL,13,FIn a report published on Wednesday,
OL,14,Fthe Commons Public Accounts Committee
OL,15,F(PAC) found the cost of collecting
OL,16,Ftaxes rose by #563 million over the
OL,17,Flast parliament, while productivity
OL,18,Ffell despite HMRC employing more
OL,19,Fsenior staff.
