OL,3,C'Lumbering dinosaur' HMRC becoming
OL,4,Cmore expensive and less trusted, say
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FBefore the Covid-19 pandemic, HMRC's
OL,8,Fcompliance work retuned more than #1.4
OL,9,Fmillion per member of staff, but this
OL,10,Ffigure has since fallen to #1.27
OL,11,Fmillion despite investments meant to
OL,12,Fimprove productivity.
OL,14,FAt the same time, the committee warned
OL,15,Fthat "taxpayers' trust in HMRC is
OL,16,Ffalling, which could affect their
OL,17,Fwillingness to meet their obligations
OL,18,Fto pay the right amount of tax on
OL,19,Ftime".
