OL,3,C'Lumbering dinosaur' HMRC becoming
OL,4,Cmore expensive and less trusted, say
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FMPs also criticised HMRC's slow
OL,8,Fprogress in transforming its IT
OL,9,Fsystems, with PAC chairman Sir
OL,10,FGeoffrey Clifton-Brown calling it a
OL,11,F"lumbering dinosaur" that still relies
OL,12,Fheavily on communicating by post.
OL,14,FAround 70% of HMRC's correspondence is
OL,15,Fdone by post, which the committee said
OL,16,Fis "inconvenient and costly" and
OL,17,Fdeters people from using its digital
OL,18,Fservices.
