OL,3,C'Lumbering dinosaur' HMRC becoming
OL,4,Cmore expensive and less trusted, say
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FSir Geoffrey said: "It is time for
OL,8,FHMRC to prioritise modernising its own
OL,9,Fsystems so that it is fit to enter the
OL,10,Fsecond quarter of the 21st century.
OL,12,F"The potential for new technologies
OL,13,Fsuch as AI (artificial intelligence)
OL,14,Fto augment HMRC's efforts to tackle
OL,15,Fthese issues is clear, and HMRC must
OL,16,Fmove at pace to seize the
OL,17,Fopportunities it presents."
