OL,3,C'Lumbering dinosaur' HMRC becoming
OL,4,Cmore expensive and less trusted, say
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FBut the committee warned that HMRC's
OL,8,Freliance on "legacy systems" means it
OL,9,Fis "not well-placed" to take advantage
OL,10,Fof opportunities presented by AI and
OL,11,Fis "more vulnerable to the use of AI
OL,12,Fby bad actors".
OL,14,FMPs urged the agency to learn lessons
OL,15,Ffrom its main digital project ` Making
OL,16,FTax Digital ` saying it had imposed
OL,17,F#300 million in extra costs on
OL,18,Fbusinesses paying VAT.
