OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FMaking Tax Digital is also expected to
OL,8,Fadd #200 million to the cost of income
OL,9,Ftax self-assessment when it is
OL,10,Fextended next year, a situation Sir
OL,11,FGeoffrey described as "completely
OL,12,Fintolerable".
OL,14,FPointing to the example of the
OL,15,FPassport Office, he said it is
OL,16,F"possible for public bodies to swiftly
OL,17,Fand radically transform their digital
OL,18,Fservices while maintaining security".
