OL,3,C'Lumbering dinosaur' HMRC becoming
OL,4,Cmore expensive and less trusted, say
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,F"If it is possible for the Passport
OL,8,FOffice to achieve these outcomes,
OL,9,Fwhich handles just as much
OL,10,Fconfidential information, then it will
OL,11,Fbe possible for HMRC to learn the
OL,12,Flessons and do the same," he added.
OL,14,FWednesday's report is the second from
OL,15,Fthe PAC this year to criticise HMRC,
OL,16,Fwith the committee finding in January
OL,17,Fthat deteriorating services were
OL,18,Feroding trust in the system.
