OL,3,C'Lumbering dinosaur' HMRC becoming
OL,4,Cmore expensive and less trusted, say
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FAn HMRC spokesman said: "It costs HMRC
OL,8,Fjust half a penny to collect every
OL,9,Fpound of tax revenue and the National
OL,10,FAudit Office has said our compliance
OL,11,Fwork provides good value for money.
OL,13,F"As part of the Government's plan for
OL,14,Fchange, we're investing to modernise
OL,15,Fand reform the tax system, determined
OL,16,Fto reduce costs and the tax gap as we
OL,17,Fimprove our compliance and customer
OL,18,Fservices further."
